Text: See diagram for specific set-up locations.
Set-up 1 study table (skirted) outside the room with 2 chairs for registration.
Make sure to turn the projector off at the end of the event.
Please do a sound check prior to client's arrival.
Please remember to lock the touchscreen.
Client should arrive to begin setting up the room.
Event should end. Load out will begin.
Load out should be complete. Turn off projector & raise screen. Put away
microphones & collect small AV equipment that was used (slide advancer, etc.). Check
for any lost and found items (note in daily report and take to SM). Cleaning: Remove
trash from MPR, vacuum, & wipe down counters & tables.
